data.description: First floor flat of approximately 1,206 square feet featuring one bedroom, den (Could be second BR), two bathrooms, living room, dining room, a laundry closet; kitchen. A broom finish concrete patio is located off the living room which is totally enclosed by a vinyl fence, with matching gate. An exterior storage shed is adjacent to the patio. Additionally, these units are built with cable outlets, as well as pre-wire for ceiling fans, as shown on the pre-wire floor plans. Resort style amenities including pool, kayak launch, meditation areas, clubhouse with kitchen, work out room, kids area, out door movie theater and more. Located just minutes from Peninsula Town Center, quick access to interstates 64, 264 and 664. Located minutes from Bass Pro shop off Power Plant Pkwy.
